  "rationale": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice D is correct. It's given that <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"f left parenthesis x right parenthesis equals x plus 6\"><mi>f</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn></math>. Substituting <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"2\"><mn>2</mn></math> for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi></math> in the function <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"f\"><mi>f</mi></math> yields <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"f left parenthesis 2 right parenthesis equals 2 plus 6\"><mi>f</mi><mo>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn></math>, or <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"f left parenthesis 2 right parenthesis equals 8\"><mi>f</mi><mo>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>8</mn></math>. It's also given that <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"g left parenthesis x right parenthesis equals 6 x\"><mi>g</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn><mi>x</mi></math>. Substituting <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"2\"><mn>2</mn></math> for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi></math> in the function <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"g\"><mi>g</mi></math> yields <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"g left parenthesis 2 right parenthesis equals left parenthesis 6 right parenthesis left parenthesis 2 right parenthesis\"><mi>g</mi><mo>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>)</mo></math>, or <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"g left parenthesis 2 right parenthesis equals 12\"><mi>g</mi><mfenced><mn>2</mn></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>12</mn></math>. Substituting <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.o